Package de.jvstvshd.localstream.network.handling

Class PacketHandler.BasicImpl

java.lang.Object
de.jvstvshd.localstream.network.handling.PacketHandler.BasicImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
PacketClientHandler, PacketHandler, PacketServerHandler
Enclosing interface:
PacketHandler
public static final class PacketHandler.BasicImpl extends Object implements PacketClientHandler, PacketServerHandler
A basic implementation of PacketClientHandler and PacketServerHandler to avoid NPEs, to give more informative errors and may also to set a correct handler. If one handle... method is called, a real handler is searched and may get set if no errors occur.

DO NOT USE THIS AT RUNTIME! REALLY NOT
